It is a good Telugu movie but my suggestion to the Director, Writer and 
Producer is
that
1) It is unnecessary to kill the Hero at the end and by so doing it 
projected that  Kabaddi is a violent game and people can get killed !  
It discourages youngsters to take up the game seriously.

rural youngsters to take up the game as grameena jattulu. Excellent 
idea. But suudenly the hero is killed by a player's kick. Probably the 
Director thought that by making it a tragedy he can draw more viewers; I 
think it has done more harm than good to the game and  to the film.

know that this place has a beautiful beach, INS Kalinga, yerra dibbalu etc.
